snippet.title: The Death Forest Walkthrough
snippet.description:
This is a guide on how to beat the game.
Oil: Located in the shack below the cliff and house.
Tire: Located in the tunnel-like maze.
Gasoline: Located in the cave near the rock path or in the forest area with plants and trees.
Spark plug: Located in the house on the cliff. 
Unlock the fence house before getting all items, and on the motorcycle, do not hit any debris such as rocks, planks, metal, or anything else if you do it's a game over.
Download Link:
https://www.freem.ne.jp/win/game/7158
